<subSubSection id="63CC169418FEF64EBB0128F139A7410C" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" type="remarks">
<paragraph id="BF40A4D11F1F4F09FE118DCFC2A72137" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Remarks.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="B5B9F5BC0470E323C9010E2692E7741C" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
<bibRefCitation id="FC2BD860F123F2AC0309A93A0E54B053" author="Gistel, JNFX" journalOrPublisher="Schorner, Straubing" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" refId="B90" refString="Gistel, JNFX, 1857. Achthundert und zwanzig neue oder unbeschriebene wirbellose Thiere. Schorner, Straubing" title="Achthundert und zwanzig neue oder unbeschriebene wirbellose Thiere." year="1857">Gistel (1857)</bibRefCitation>
provided a very brief Latin description of this species which he compared to 
<taxonomicName id="70EDECA2D2548C53160092538DAB32DC" class="Insecta" genus="P." higherTaxonomySource="GBIF,CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="P. glauca" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="glauca">
<emphasis id="960DD06F7CA56A78293389936002ED10" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">P. glauca</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. 
<taxonomicName id="114D7420A63190C80478F98CE1F0A5A1" authorityName="Gistel" authorityYear="1857" class="Insecta" family="Scarabaeidae" genus="Pelidnota" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Pelidnota fallax" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fallax">
<emphasis id="01FC8C99F0E60A8C043001783927C6D1" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Pelidnota fallax</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was described as being brass-green in color (
<bibRefCitation id="11AD32B3D57AA3F8E1A54942B3AB4AB3" author="Gistel, JNFX" journalOrPublisher="Schorner, Straubing" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" refId="B90" refString="Gistel, JNFX, 1857. Achthundert und zwanzig neue oder unbeschriebene wirbellose Thiere. Schorner, Straubing" title="Achthundert und zwanzig neue oder unbeschriebene wirbellose Thiere." year="1857">Gistel 1857</bibRefCitation>
). The pronotum is &quot;glittering copper-green&quot; with yellow edges (
<bibRefCitation id="A49FB95342D1C86C317D3A14C38A6C9C" author="Gistel, JNFX" journalOrPublisher="Schorner, Straubing" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" refId="B90" refString="Gistel, JNFX, 1857. Achthundert und zwanzig neue oder unbeschriebene wirbellose Thiere. Schorner, Straubing" title="Achthundert und zwanzig neue oder unbeschriebene wirbellose Thiere." year="1857">Gistel 1857</bibRefCitation>
). This species was not included in catalogs of world 
<taxonomicName id="BD9C249D376E51247000405D994830C0" authorityName="MacLeay" authorityYear="1819" lsidName="" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" rank="subFamily" subFamily="Rutelinae">Rutelinae</taxonomicName>
(
<bibRefCitation id="D612181A29EED364973CB3896EB3391F" author="Ohaus, F" journalOrPublisher="Coleopterorum Catalogus" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" pagination="1 - 241" refId="B278" refString="Ohaus, F, 1918. Scarabaeidae: Euchirinae, Phaenomerinae, Rutelinae. Coleopterorum Catalogus 20: 1 - 241" title="Scarabaeidae: Euchirinae, Phaenomerinae, Rutelinae." volume="20" year="1918">Ohaus 1918</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="9203C0E93AF7CFA96CDE118D36F7747F" author="Ohaus, F" journalOrPublisher="Mitteilungen der Deutschen Entomologischen Gesellschaft" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" refId="B286" refString="Ohaus, F, 1934b. Coleopteralamellicornia, Fam. Scarabaeidae, Subfam. Rutelinae. T.1: Tribus Rutelini. Genera Insectorum Fasc. 199A: 1-172." title="Coleopteralamellicornia, Fam. Scarabaeidae, Subfam. Rutelinae. T. 1: Tribus Rutelini. Genera Insectorum Fasc. 199 A: 1 - 172." year="1934 b">1934b</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="1372B049E1B938561437E83BA8214AF6" author="Machatschke, JW" journalOrPublisher="Coleopterorum Catalogus Supplementa" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" pagination="1 - 361" refId="B188" refString="Machatschke, JW, 1972. Scarabaeoidea: Melolonthidae, Rutelinae. Coleopterorum Catalogus Supplementa 66: 1 - 361" title="Scarabaeoidea: Melolonthidae, Rutelinae." volume="66" year="1972">Machatschke 1972</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="800A6D34BD8558AC52EABCD72C09DD2D" author="Machatschke, JW" journalOrPublisher="Coleopterorum Catalogus Supplementa" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" pagination="363 - 429" refId="B189" refString="Machatschke, JW, 1974. Scarabaeoidea: Melolonthidae, Rutelinae. Coleopterorum Catalogus Supplementa 66: 363 - 429" title="Scarabaeoidea: Melolonthidae, Rutelinae." volume="66" year="1974">1974</bibRefCitation>
). 
<bibRefCitation id="C76C5C6EF0605D455032880546CE9EBA" author="Krajcik, M" journalOrPublisher="Berliner Entomologische Zeitschrift" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" refId="B155" refString="Krajcik, M, 2008. Animma. X. Supplement 4. Checklist of the Scarabaeoidea of the World. 2. Rutelinae (Coleoptera: Scarabaeidae: Rutelinae). Second Edition. Plzen, 142 pp." title="Animma. X. Supplement 4. Checklist of the Scarabaeoidea of the World. 2. Rutelinae (Coleoptera: Scarabaeidae: Rutelinae). Second Edition. Plzen, 142 pp." year="2008">Krajcik (2008)</bibRefCitation>
correctly listed 
<taxonomicName id="30C70F87D4DC44947625D58124BDCD75" class="Insecta" genus="P." higherTaxonomySource="GBIF,CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="P. fallax" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fallax">
<emphasis id="402FBA0145158528640A5B0CC846B90D" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">P. fallax</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as a valid species. We have not examined the type specimen of this species and the validity of this taxon is unknown to us. Because 
<taxonomicName id="84DAEA518EB0ED1D0000BCF7C9AA569C" class="Insecta" genus="P." higherTaxonomySource="GBIF,CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="P. fallax" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fallax">
<emphasis id="F3204EF21D4910A868DB62834B359F98" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">P. fallax</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was compared to 
<taxonomicName id="4FB9EB20B5E61A62D5DB2B4EB479AF77" class="Insecta" genus="P." higherTaxonomySource="GBIF,CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="P. glauca" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="glauca">
<emphasis id="6ACB231890635EDE096E352A54571679" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">P. glauca</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(synonym of 
<taxonomicName id="0631B8F78C4D181D46BAD5C97A21857B" class="Insecta" genus="P." higherTaxonomySource="GBIF,CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="P. alliacea" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="alliacea">
<emphasis id="C2D1FD992FE59248F8F36EEBEB2FF98C" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">P. alliacea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
[Germar]) by 
<bibRefCitation id="132F21372F04E90EC97F04C8F55D3BA9" author="Gistel, JNFX" journalOrPublisher="Schorner, Straubing" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" refId="B90" refString="Gistel, JNFX, 1857. Achthundert und zwanzig neue oder unbeschriebene wirbellose Thiere. Schorner, Straubing" title="Achthundert und zwanzig neue oder unbeschriebene wirbellose Thiere." year="1857">Gistel (1857)</bibRefCitation>
, examination of the type specimen (possibly lost) of 
<taxonomicName id="FA24ADAA6A9BDAF517F181A3E75709FC" class="Insecta" genus="P." higherTaxonomySource="GBIF,CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="P. fallax" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fallax">
<emphasis id="96BEBE69AA0C9C6F2EA287EA145F8940" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">P. fallax</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Gistel could be important for stabilizing the taxonomy and nomenclature of species previously compared to 
<taxonomicName id="BB557232A727DD08D8F321DF5BADEC7D" class="Insecta" genus="P." higherTaxonomySource="GBIF,CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="P. aeruginosa" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="aeruginosa">
<emphasis id="0F843DA481ED63F6C9AA2E17281A723A" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">P. aeruginosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Linnaeus).
</paragraph>
